name: S.I.D.F.T.A. - The Story of A Longing Algorithm Above The Sky of Boncang City
description: S.I.D.F.T.A. stands for "Senja Indah di Future Tanah Abang". From the Indonesian language which means "Beautiful Dusk in the Future of Tanah Abang". A chillwave/chillgaze/synth style music project whose song content tells the daily life in a future cyber city called Boncang. In the universe not far from our universe.  This one is the first track I chose as NFT. I release it in audio visual form with pixel art animation style.  Please enjoy.
